{"tid":488274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★植入程式碼　盜用瀏覽者電腦 黑客騎劫親子王國掘虛擬幣","createTime":"2017-12-03T14:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T06:29:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"73111cef2eb991187539cbe751afd3c53f17497d","tid":488274,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:23:22.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》發現本港首次有網站包括「親子王國」疑遭黑客入侵，黑客在其網頁植入「掘礦程式碼」，令市民瀏覽該網站時，在不知情下電腦遭人盜用大量運算能力，黑客藉此掘礦賺取新興虛擬貨幣「門羅幣（Monero）」圖利。親子王國承認曾發現網站遭植入掘礦程式碼，表示已移除並更新防火牆加強保安。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》日前測試時，發現瀏覽親子王國時，網頁原始碼顯示內含掘礦程式碼，<a href=\"http://令瀏覽者電腦會接駁到crypto-loot.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BB%A4%E7%80%8F%E8%A6%BD%E8%80%85%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E6%9C%83%E6%8E%A5%E9%A7%81%E5%88%B0crypto-loot.com&d=I9P2errRHAQm9SPCg6XOjwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=da115dc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">令瀏覽者電腦會接駁到crypto-loot.com</a>網站協助掘礦，掘礦得益被存入匿名的賬戶，其間網站或防病毒預軟未有出警告。測試時電腦處理器及記憶體使用率明顯上升，由正常僅佔用中央處理器（CPU）5%或以下的運算能力，一度飆升至佔用10至30%，電腦反應亦變得遲鈍，但至周三親子王國掘礦程式碼已被移除。該掘礦網站crypto-loot在簡介，明言只要在網站植入其指定程式碼，即可取用對方瀏覽者電腦的運算能力，從而賺取虛擬貨幣門羅幣，又強調隱蔽度頗高，不易被對方發現，但表明責任由使用者自負。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171203/20233090\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171203%2F20233090&d=I9P2errRHAQm9SPCg6XOjwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=ed01b7bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171203%2F20233090&h=b33fc6ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171203/20233090</a>"},{"pid":"dee45e69496860eec79b34e8b9698513fda219a0","tid":488274,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30e2593facad9d26024eccbf94e6b104a39d72d","tid":488274,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T16:02:07.000Z","msg":"老貓成日上親子王國"},{"pid":"0c54a175be31ba2ffc4e854bb83221b8c5ae0920","tid":488274,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T16:03:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老貓成日上親子王國</blockquote><br />\nJ c9"},{"pid":"4d266cd18724824605c5fb03e69863ab3a8925ac","tid":488274,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T16:14:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老貓成日上親子王國</blockquote><br />\nJ c9</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8569ef92a17df2b955f1e0946569b7ac8a89a9c9","tid":488274,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T17:19:08.000Z","msg":"😳小妹啲人妻fd日日上"},{"pid":"36ad91f5117da29be6d6c73b43321c16dd7ba155","tid":488274,"uid":126897,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T17:22:48.000Z","msg":"有冇可能係自己植入? 真係咁易比人hack?"},{"pid":"36867a9c0a13da36f22468aeee02b18e53a06d1b","tid":488274,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T17:25:06.000Z","msg":"baby condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfffbe17f0f8ec965f5e5e39e17a6580acb3d58d","tid":488274,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T17:32:39.000Z","msg":"It =發達"},{"pid":"05369a871753196f48fc505fac24a61d720a46b7","tid":488274,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T06:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老貓成日上親子王國</blockquote><br />\nJ c9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc116dd1b6365408cf49d3da6eea37072fdb6685","tid":488274,"uid":117901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T06:29:35.000Z","msg":"話唔定連登app都有"}]}